{
  "video_id": "Qhomjw2P-V0",
  "title": "What really motivates people to be honest in business | Alexander Wagner",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12580.0,
      "end_time": 16200.0,
      "text": "How many companies have you interacted with today?"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 17600.0,
      "end_time": 18715.0,
      "text": "Well, you got up in the morning,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 18740.0,
      "end_time": 19955.0,
      "text": "took a shower,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 19980.0,
      "end_time": 21236.0,
      "text": "washed your hair,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 21260.0,
      "end_time": 22796.0,
      "text": "used a hair dryer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 22820.0,
      "end_time": 24360.0,
      "text": "ate breakfast --"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 24600.0,
      "end_time": 25918.0,
      "text": "ate cereals, fruit, yogurt, whatever --"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 25942.0,
      "end_time": 27156.0,
      "text": "had coffee --"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 27180.0,
      "end_time": 28556.0,
      "text": "tea."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 28580.0,
      "end_time": 30555.0,
      "text": "You took public transport to come here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 30580.0,
      "end_time": 32420.0,
      "text": "or maybe used your private car."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 33340.0,
      "end_time": 36900.0,
      "text": "You interacted with the company that you work for or that you own."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 37980.0,
      "end_time": 39940.0,
      "text": "You interacted with your clients,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 40580.0,
      "end_time": 41780.0,
      "text": "your customers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 42460.0,
      "end_time": 43716.0,
      "text": "and so on and so forth."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 43740.0,
      "end_time": 47356.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m pretty sure there are at least seven companies"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 47380.0,
      "end_time": 49140.0,
      "text": "you&#39;ve interacted with today."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 49780.0,
      "end_time": 51780.0,
      "text": "Let me tell you a stunning statistic."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 52660.0,
      "end_time": 57350.0,
      "text": "One out of seven large, public corporations"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 57600.0,
      "end_time": 59300.0,
      "text": "commit fraud every year."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 60220.0,
      "end_time": 63635.0,
      "text": "This is a US academic study that looks at US companies --"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 63660.0,
      "end_time": 66860.0,
      "text": "I have no reason to believe that it&#39;s different in Europe."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 67300.0,
      "end_time": 71515.0,
      "text": "This is a study that looks at both detected and undetected fraud"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 71540.0,
      "end_time": 73276.0,
      "text": "using statistical methods."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 73300.0,
      "end_time": 75200.0,
      "text": "This is not petty fraud."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 75940.0,
      "end_time": 78795.0,
      "text": "These frauds cost the shareholders of these companies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 78820.0,
      "end_time": 80760.0,
      "text": "and therefore society,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 80100.0,
      "end_time": 83699.0,
      "text": "on the order of 380 billion dollars per year."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 84780.0,
      "end_time": 86996.0,
      "text": "We can all think of some examples, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 87200.0,
      "end_time": 90820.0,
      "text": "The car industry&#39;s secrets aren&#39;t quite so secret anymore."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 91620.0,
      "end_time": 94916.0,
      "text": "Fraud has become a feature,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 94940.0,
      "end_time": 96155.0,
      "text": "not a bug,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 96180.0,
      "end_time": 98116.0,
      "text": "of the financial services industry."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 98140.0,
      "end_time": 100356.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s not me who&#39;s claiming that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 100380.0,
      "end_time": 103636.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s the president of the American Finance Association"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 103660.0,
      "end_time": 106596.0,
      "text": "who stated that in his presidential address."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 106620.0,
      "end_time": 109356.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s a huge problem if you think about, especially,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 109380.0,
      "end_time": 111760.0,
      "text": "an economy like Switzerland,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 111100.0,
      "end_time": 115300.0,
      "text": "which relies so much on the trust put into its financial industry."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 116780.0,
      "end_time": 117996.0,
      "text": "On the other hand,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 118200.0,
      "end_time": 121556.0,
      "text": "there are six out of seven companies who actually remain honest"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 121580.0,
      "end_time": 125420.0,
      "text": "despite all temptations to start engaging in fraud."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 126600.0,
      "end_time": 128356.0,
      "text": "There are whistle-blowers like Michael Woodford,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 128380.0,
      "end_time": 130716.0,
      "text": "who blew the whistle on Olympus."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 130740.00000000001,
      "end_time": 133436.0,
      "text": "These whistle-blowers risk their careers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 133460.0,
      "end_time": 134676.0,
      "text": "their friendships,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 134700.0,
      "end_time": 136835.0,
      "text": "to bring out the truth about their companies."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 136860.0,
      "end_time": 139476.0,
      "text": "There are journalists like Anna Politkovskaya"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 139500.0,
      "end_time": 143356.0,
      "text": "who risk even their lives to report human rights violations."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 143380.0,
      "end_time": 144596.0,
      "text": "She got killed --"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 144620.0,
      "end_time": 145836.0,
      "text": "every year,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 145860.0,
      "end_time": 147516.0,
      "text": "around 100 journalists get killed"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 147540.0,
      "end_time": 150260.0,
      "text": "because of their conviction to bring out the truth."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 151860.0,
      "end_time": 153116.0,
      "text": "So in my talk today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 153140.0,
      "end_time": 156636.0,
      "text": "I want to share with you some insights I&#39;ve obtained and learned"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 156660.0,
      "end_time": 159956.0,
      "text": "in the last 10 years of conducting research in this."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 159980.0,
      "end_time": 163476.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m a researcher, a scientist working with economists,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 163500.0,
      "end_time": 164836.0,
      "text": "financial economists,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 164860.0,
      "end_time": 166916.0,
      "text": "ethicists, neuroscientists,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 166940.0,
      "end_time": 168276.0,
      "text": "lawyers and others"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 168300.0,
      "end_time": 170396.0,
      "text": "trying to understand what makes humans tick,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 170420.0,
      "end_time": 175196.0,
      "text": "and how can we address this issue of fraud in corporations"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 175220.0,
      "end_time": 178380.0,
      "text": "and therefore contribute to the improvement of the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 179100.0,
      "end_time": 182636.0,
      "text": "I want to start by sharing with you two very distinct visions"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 182660.0,
      "end_time": 184476.0,
      "text": "of how people behave."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 184500.0,
      "end_time": 186340.0,
      "text": "First, meet Adam Smith,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 187200.0,
      "end_time": 188980.0,
      "text": "founding father of modern economics."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 190100.0,
      "end_time": 194396.0,
      "text": "His basic idea was that if everybody behaves in their own self-interests,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 194420.0,
      "end_time": 196940.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s good for everybody in the end."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 197900.0,
      "end_time": 200956.0,
      "text": "Self-interest isn&#39;t a narrowly defined concept"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 200980.0,
      "end_time": 202916.0,
      "text": "just for your immediate utility."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 202940.0,
      "end_time": 204876.0,
      "text": "It has a long-run implication."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 204900.0,
      "end_time": 206380.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s think about that."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 206900.0,
      "end_time": 208916.0,
      "text": "Think about this dog here."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 208940.0,
      "end_time": 210140.0,
      "text": "That might be us."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 211260.0,
      "end_time": 212516.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s this temptation --"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 212540.0,
      "end_time": 214916.0,
      "text": "I apologize to all vegetarians, but --"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 214940.0,
      "end_time": 215956.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 215980.0,
      "end_time": 217676.0,
      "text": "Dogs do like the bratwurst."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 217700.0,
      "end_time": 220760.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 220100.0,
      "end_time": 223196.0,
      "text": "Now, the straight-up, self-interested move here"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 223220.0,
      "end_time": 224796.0,
      "text": "is to go for that."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 224820.0,
      "end_time": 227756.0,
      "text": "So my friend Adam here might jump up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 227780.0,
      "end_time": 231140.0,
      "text": "get the sausage and thereby ruin all this beautiful tableware."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 231820.0,
      "end_time": 233636.0,
      "text": "But that&#39;s not what Adam Smith meant."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 233660.0,
      "end_time": 236316.0,
      "text": "He didn&#39;t mean disregard all consequences --"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 236340.0,
      "end_time": 237556.0,
      "text": "to the contrary."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 237580.0,
      "end_time": 238836.0,
      "text": "He would have thought,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 238860.0,
      "end_time": 240876.0,
      "text": "well, there may be negative consequences,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 240900.0,
      "end_time": 242116.0,
      "text": "for example,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 242140.0,
      "end_time": 245236.0,
      "text": "the owner might be angry with the dog"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 245260.0,
      "end_time": 248859.0,
      "text": "and the dog, anticipating that, might not behave in this way."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 249660.0,
      "end_time": 250916.0,
      "text": "That might be us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 250940.0,
      "end_time": 253996.0,
      "text": "weighing the benefits and costs of our actions."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 254200.0,
      "end_time": 255260.0,
      "text": "How does that play out?"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 255780.0,
      "end_time": 257756.0,
      "text": "Well, many of you, I&#39;m sure,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 257779.0,
      "end_time": 259315.0,
      "text": "have in your companies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 259339.0,
      "end_time": 261155.0,
      "text": "especially if it&#39;s a large company,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 261180.0,
      "end_time": 262836.0,
      "text": "a code of conduct."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 262860.0,
      "end_time": 266276.0,
      "text": "And then if you behave according to that code of conduct,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 266300.0,
      "end_time": 269476.0,
      "text": "that improves your chances of getting a bonus payment."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 269500.0,
      "end_time": 271635.0,
      "text": "And on the other hand, if you disregard it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 271659.0,
      "end_time": 274396.0,
      "text": "then there are higher chances of not getting your bonus"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 274420.0,
      "end_time": 275956.0,
      "text": "or its being diminished."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 275980.0,
      "end_time": 277236.0,
      "text": "In other words,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 277260.0,
      "end_time": 279750.0,
      "text": "this is a very economic motivation"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 279100.0,
      "end_time": 281876.0,
      "text": "of trying to get people to be more honest,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 281900.0,
      "end_time": 285260.0,
      "text": "or more aligned with the corporation&#39;s principles."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 286600.0,
      "end_time": 291316.0,
      "text": "Similarly, reputation is a very powerful economic force, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 291340.0,
      "end_time": 292876.0,
      "text": "We try to build a reputation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 292900.0,
      "end_time": 294316.0,
      "text": "maybe for being honest,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 294340.0,
      "end_time": 296739.0,
      "text": "because then people trust us more in the future."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 297780.0,
      "end_time": 298996.0,
      "text": "Right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 299200.0,
      "end_time": 301116.0,
      "text": "Adam Smith talked about the baker"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 301140.0,
      "end_time": 304916.0,
      "text": "who&#39;s not producing good bread out of his benevolence"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 304940.0,
      "end_time": 307956.0,
      "text": "for those people who consume the bread,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 307980.0,
      "end_time": 311200.0,
      "text": "but because he wants to sell more future bread."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 311980.0,
      "end_time": 314196.0,
      "text": "In my research, we find, for example,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 314220.0,
      "end_time": 315596.0,
      "text": "at the University of Zurich,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 315620.0,
      "end_time": 319820.0,
      "text": "that Swiss banks who get caught up in media,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 320540.0,
      "end_time": 322316.0,
      "text": "and in the context, for example,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 322340.0,
      "end_time": 323876.0,
      "text": "of tax evasion, of tax fraud,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 323900.0,
      "end_time": 325635.0,
      "text": "have bad media coverage."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 325660.0,
      "end_time": 328396.0,
      "text": "They lose net new money in the future"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 328420.0,
      "end_time": 330360.0,
      "text": "and therefore make lower profits."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 330600.0,
      "end_time": 332420.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s a very powerful reputational force."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 334200.0,
      "end_time": 335620.0,
      "text": "Benefits and costs."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 336940.0,
      "end_time": 339516.0,
      "text": "Here&#39;s another viewpoint of the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 339540.0,
      "end_time": 341760.0,
      "text": "Meet Immanuel Kant,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 341100.0,
      "end_time": 343860.0,
      "text": "18th-century German philosopher superstar."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 344740.0,
      "end_time": 346356.0,
      "text": "He developed this notion"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 346380.0,
      "end_time": 349516.0,
      "text": "that independent of the consequences,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 349540.0,
      "end_time": 352516.0,
      "text": "some actions are just right"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 352540.0,
      "end_time": 354236.0,
      "text": "and some are just wrong."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 354260.0,
      "end_time": 357476.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s just wrong to lie, for example."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 357500.0,
      "end_time": 360636.0,
      "text": "So, meet my friend Immanuel here."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 360660.0,
      "end_time": 363476.0,
      "text": "He knows that the sausage is very tasty,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 363500.0,
      "end_time": 365956.0,
      "text": "but he&#39;s going to turn away because he&#39;s a good dog."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 365980.0,
      "end_time": 368676.0,
      "text": "He knows it&#39;s wrong to jump up"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 368700.0,
      "end_time": 371500.0,
      "text": "and risk ruining all this beautiful tableware."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 372340.0,
      "end_time": 374756.0,
      "text": "If you believe that people are motivated like that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 374780.0,
      "end_time": 376955.0,
      "text": "then all the stuff about incentives,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 376980.0,
      "end_time": 380756.0,
      "text": "all the stuff about code of conduct and bonus systems and so on,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 380780.0,
      "end_time": 382955.0,
      "text": "doesn&#39;t make a whole lot of sense."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 382980.0,
      "end_time": 387156.0,
      "text": "People are motivated by different values perhaps."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 387180.0,
      "end_time": 390556.0,
      "text": "So, what are people actually motivated by?"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 390580.0,
      "end_time": 392756.0,
      "text": "These two gentlemen here have perfect hairdos,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 392780.0,
      "end_time": 397260.0,
      "text": "but they give us very different views of the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 397660.0,
      "end_time": 398916.0,
      "text": "What do we do with this?"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 398940.0,
      "end_time": 400596.0,
      "text": "Well, I&#39;m an economist"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 400620.0,
      "end_time": 404796.0,
      "text": "and we conduct so-called experiments to address this issue."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 404820.0,
      "end_time": 408116.0,
      "text": "We strip away facts which are confusing in reality."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 408140.0,
      "end_time": 410876.0,
      "text": "Reality is so rich, there is so much going on,"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 410900.0,
      "end_time": 414859.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s almost impossible to know what drives people&#39;s behavior really."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 415340.0,
      "end_time": 418600.0,
      "text": "So let&#39;s do a little experiment together."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 418500.0,
      "end_time": 421100.0,
      "text": "Imagine the following situation."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 422220.0,
      "end_time": 424636.0,
      "text": "You&#39;re in a room alone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 424660.0,
      "end_time": 426196.0,
      "text": "not like here."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 426220.0,
      "end_time": 429660.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s a five-franc coin like the one I&#39;m holding up right now"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 430380.0,
      "end_time": 431956.0,
      "text": "in front of you."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 431980.0,
      "end_time": 433556.0,
      "text": "Here are your instructions:"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 433580.0,
      "end_time": 436600.0,
      "text": "toss the coin four times,"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 437620.0,
      "end_time": 440360.0,
      "text": "and then on a computer terminal in front of you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 440600.0,
      "end_time": 443716.0,
      "text": "enter the number of times tails came up."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 443740.0,
      "end_time": 445200.0,
      "text": "This is the situation."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 445540.0,
      "end_time": 446756.0,
      "text": "Here&#39;s the rub."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 446780.0,
      "end_time": 450155.0,
      "text": "For every time that you announce that you had a tails throw,"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 450180.0,
      "end_time": 451676.0,
      "text": "you get paid five francs."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 451700.0,
      "end_time": 454236.0,
      "text": "So if you say I had two tails throws,"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 454260.0,
      "end_time": 456476.0,
      "text": "you get paid 10 francs."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 456500.0,
      "end_time": 459436.0,
      "text": "If you say you had zero, you get paid zero francs."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 459460.0,
      "end_time": 461916.0,
      "text": "If you say, \"I had four tails throws,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 461940.0,
      "end_time": 463956.0,
      "text": "then you get paid 20 francs."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 463980.0,
      "end_time": 465236.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s anonymous,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 465260.0,
      "end_time": 467156.0,
      "text": "nobody&#39;s watching what you&#39;re doing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 467180.0,
      "end_time": 469516.0,
      "text": "and you get paid that money anonymously."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 469540.0,
      "end_time": 471170.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve got two questions for you."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 471580.0,
      "end_time": 473195.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 473220.0,
      "end_time": 474860.0,
      "text": "You know what&#39;s coming now, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 475820.0,
      "end_time": 479300.0,
      "text": "First, how would you behave in that situation?"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 480600.0,
      "end_time": 482996.0,
      "text": "The second, look to your left and look to your right --"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 483200.0,
      "end_time": 484360.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 484600.0,
      "end_time": 486436.0,
      "text": "and think about how the person sitting next to you"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 486460.0,
      "end_time": 488116.0,
      "text": "might behave in that situation."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 488140.0,
      "end_time": 490276.0,
      "text": "We did this experiment for real."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 490300.0,
      "end_time": 492996.0,
      "text": "We did it at the Manifesta art exhibition"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 493200.0,
      "end_time": 495476.0,
      "text": "that took place here in Zurich recently,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 495500.0,
      "end_time": 498356.0,
      "text": "not with students in the lab at the university"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 498380.0,
      "end_time": 500156.0,
      "text": "but with the real population,"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 500180.0,
      "end_time": 501380.0,
      "text": "like you guys."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 501900.0,
      "end_time": 504360.0,
      "text": "First, a quick reminder of stats."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 504600.0,
      "end_time": 507636.0,
      "text": "If I throw the coin four times and it&#39;s a fair coin,"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 507660.0,
      "end_time": 511756.0,
      "text": "then the probability that it comes up four times tails"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 511780.0,
      "end_time": 514179.0,
      "text": "is 6.25 percent."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 514900.0,
      "end_time": 516555.0,
      "text": "And I hope you can intuitively see"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 516580.00000000006,
      "end_time": 519956.00000000006,
      "text": "that the probability that all four of them are tails is much lower"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 519980.0,
      "end_time": 522100.0,
      "text": "than if two of them are tails, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 522580.00000000006,
      "end_time": 524200.00000000006,
      "text": "Here are the specific numbers."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 525859.0,
      "end_time": 527355.0,
      "text": "Here&#39;s what happened."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 527379.0,
      "end_time": 529580.0,
      "text": "People did this experiment for real."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 530619.0,
      "end_time": 533955.0,
      "text": "Around 30 to 35 percent of people said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 533979.0,
      "end_time": 536380.0,
      "text": "\"Well, I had four tails throws.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 537460.0,
      "end_time": 539276.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s extremely unlikely."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 539300.0,
      "end_time": 541236.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 541260.0,
      "end_time": 544396.0,
      "text": "But the really amazing thing here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 544420.0,
      "end_time": 545716.0,
      "text": "perhaps to an economist,"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 545740.0,
      "end_time": 552276.0,
      "text": "is there are around 65 percent of people who did not say I had four tails throws,"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 552300.0,
      "end_time": 554476.0,
      "text": "even though in that situation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 554500.0,
      "end_time": 556596.0,
      "text": "nobody&#39;s watching you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 556620.0,
      "end_time": 558556.0,
      "text": "the only consequence that&#39;s in place"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 558580.0,
      "end_time": 561916.0,
      "text": "is you get more money if you say four than less."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 561940.0,
      "end_time": 565220.0,
      "text": "You leave 20 francs on the table by announcing zero."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 565860.0,
      "end_time": 568436.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t know whether the other people all were honest"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 568460.0,
      "end_time": 571916.0,
      "text": "or whether they also said a little bit higher or lower than what they did"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 571940.0,
      "end_time": 573156.0,
      "text": "because it&#39;s anonymous."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 573180.0,
      "end_time": 574835.0,
      "text": "We only observed the distribution."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 574860.0,
      "end_time": 577516.0,
      "text": "But what I can tell you -- and here&#39;s another coin toss."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 577540.0,
      "end_time": 579360.0,
      "text": "There you go, it&#39;s tails."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 579600.0,
      "end_time": 580555.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 580580.0,
      "end_time": 582360.0,
      "text": "Don&#39;t check, OK?"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 582600.0,
      "end_time": 584876.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 584900.0,
      "end_time": 586196.0,
      "text": "What I can tell you"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 586220.0,
      "end_time": 590660.0,
      "text": "is that not everybody behaved like Adam Smith would have predicted."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 592660.0,
      "end_time": 594236.0,
      "text": "So what does that leave us with?"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 594260.0,
      "end_time": 598756.0,
      "text": "Well, it seems people are motivated by certain intrinsic values"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 598780.0,
      "end_time": 600579.0,
      "text": "and in our research, we look at this."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 601260.0,
      "end_time": 605740.0,
      "text": "We look at the idea that people have so-called protected values."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 606580.0,
      "end_time": 609396.0,
      "text": "A protected value isn&#39;t just any value."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 609420.0,
      "end_time": 615236.0,
      "text": "A protected value is a value where you&#39;re willing to pay a price"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 615260.0,
      "end_time": 616516.0,
      "text": "to uphold that value."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 616540.0,
      "end_time": 620980.0,
      "text": "You&#39;re willing to pay a price to withstand the temptation to give in."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 622200.0,
      "end_time": 624675.0,
      "text": "And the consequence is you feel better"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 624700.0,
      "end_time": 628996.0,
      "text": "if you earn money in a way that&#39;s consistent with your values."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 629200.0,
      "end_time": 633300.0,
      "text": "Let me show you this again in the metaphor of our beloved dog here."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 634420.0,
      "end_time": 638476.0,
      "text": "If we succeed in getting the sausage without violating our values,"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 638500.0,
      "end_time": 640476.0,
      "text": "then the sausage tastes better."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 640500.0,
      "end_time": 641980.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s what our research shows."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 642540.0,
      "end_time": 643795.0,
      "text": "If, on the other hand,"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 643820.0,
      "end_time": 645760.0,
      "text": "we do so --"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 645100.0,
      "end_time": 646516.0,
      "text": "if we get the sausage"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 646540.0,
      "end_time": 649996.0,
      "text": "and in doing so we actually violate values,"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 650200.0,
      "end_time": 652996.0,
      "text": "we value the sausage less."
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 653200.0,
      "end_time": 655476.0,
      "text": "Quantitatively, that&#39;s quite powerful."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 655500.0,
      "end_time": 657956.0,
      "text": "We can measure these protected values,"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 657980.0,
      "end_time": 659196.0,
      "text": "for example,"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 659220.0,
      "end_time": 661140.0,
      "text": "by a survey measure."
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 662180.0,
      "end_time": 668156.0,
      "text": "Simple, nine-item survey that&#39;s quite predictive in these experiments."
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 668180.0,
      "end_time": 670516.0,
      "text": "If you think about the average of the population"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 670540.0,
      "end_time": 672636.0,
      "text": "and then there&#39;s a distribution around it --"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 672660.0,
      "end_time": 674699.0,
      "text": "people are different, we all are different."
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 675300.0,
      "end_time": 678276.0,
      "text": "People who have a set of protected values"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 678300.0,
      "end_time": 682476.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s one standard deviation above the average,"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 682500.0,
      "end_time": 687556.0,
      "text": "they discount money they receive by lying by about 25 percent."
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 687580.0,
      "end_time": 691196.0,
      "text": "That means a dollar received when lying"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 691220.0,
      "end_time": 693356.0,
      "text": "is worth to them only 75 cents"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 693380.0,
      "end_time": 697760.0,
      "text": "without any incentives you put in place for them to behave honestly."
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 697100.0,
      "end_time": 698836.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s their intrinsic motivation."
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 698860.0,
      "end_time": 700716.0,
      "text": "By the way, I&#39;m not a moral authority."
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 700740.0,
      "end_time": 703660.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m not saying I have all these beautiful values, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 704260.0,
      "end_time": 706196.0,
      "text": "But I&#39;m interested in how people behave"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 706220.0,
      "end_time": 709596.0,
      "text": "and how we can leverage that richness in human nature"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 709620.0,
      "end_time": 713600.0,
      "text": "to actually improve the workings of our organizations."
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 714220.0,
      "end_time": 717396.0,
      "text": "So there are two very, very different visions here."
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 717420.0,
      "end_time": 718756.0,
      "text": "On the one hand,"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 718780.0,
      "end_time": 721795.0,
      "text": "you can appeal to benefits and costs"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 721820.0,
      "end_time": 724476.0,
      "text": "and try to get people to behave according to them."
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 724500.0,
      "end_time": 726116.0,
      "text": "On the other hand,"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 726140.0,
      "end_time": 730156.0,
      "text": "you can select people who have the values"
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 730180.0,
      "end_time": 732396.0,
      "text": "and the desirable characteristics, of course --"
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 732420.0,
      "end_time": 735996.0,
      "text": "competencies that go in line with your organization."
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 736200.0,
      "end_time": 740236.0,
      "text": "I do not yet know where these protected values really come from."
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 740260.0,
      "end_time": 743636.0,
      "text": "Is it nurture or is it nature?"
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 743660.0,
      "end_time": 745360.0,
      "text": "What I can tell you"
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 745600.0,
      "end_time": 750156.0,
      "text": "is that the distribution looks pretty similar for men and women."
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 750180.0,
      "end_time": 753955.0,
      "text": "It looks pretty similar for those who had studied economics"
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 753980.0,
      "end_time": 756340.0,
      "text": "or those who had studied psychology."
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 757820.0,
      "end_time": 761196.0,
      "text": "It looks even pretty similar around different age categories"
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 761220.0,
      "end_time": 762436.0,
      "text": "among adults."
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 762460.0,
      "end_time": 765116.0,
      "text": "But I don&#39;t know yet how this develops over a lifetime."
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 765140.0,
      "end_time": 768580.0,
      "text": "That will be the subject of future research."
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 769460.0,
      "end_time": 771116.0,
      "text": "The idea I want to leave you with"
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 771140.0,
      "end_time": 773915.0,
      "text": "is it&#39;s all right to appeal to incentives."
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 773940.0,
      "end_time": 775156.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m an economist;"
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 775180.0,
      "end_time": 778990.0,
      "text": "I certainly believe in the fact that incentives work."
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 779220.0,
      "end_time": 783236.0,
      "text": "But do think about selecting the right people"
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 783260.0,
      "end_time": 786756.0,
      "text": "rather than having people and then putting incentives in place."
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 786780.0,
      "end_time": 789360.0,
      "text": "Selecting the right people with the right values"
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 789600.0,
      "end_time": 792996.0,
      "text": "may go a long way to saving a lot of trouble"
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 793200.0,
      "end_time": 794396.0,
      "text": "and a lot of money"
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 794420.0,
      "end_time": 796156.0,
      "text": "in your organizations."
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 796180.0,
      "end_time": 797435.0,
      "text": "In other words,"
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 797460.0,
      "end_time": 801220.0,
      "text": "it will pay off to put people first."
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 801860.0,
      "end_time": 803760.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 803100.0,
      "end_time": 806740.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}